          acquisition, and patron management. Here's a detailed description of
          the key features and functionalities typically found in a Library
          Management System:
        </p>
        <div
          class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start mb-4 mb-lg-3"
        >
          <form action="/signup" method="GET">
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2 fw-bold"
